sub_title: Public and Cultural Diplomacy Master's student at Università degli Studi di Siena
summary:
I'm currently in my first year of the Public and Cultural Diplomacy MA (majoring in Cultural Diplomacy) at the University of Siena. 

During my bachelor studies in New Media and Digital Culture at the University of Amsterdam, I have gained insight into many aspects of the world of media, including social networks, media content creation, media aesthetics, digital culture, digital practices, journalism, business models and big data. 

My interests include languages as well as the use of language in media, sustainable solutions, media production, and the continuous evolution of digital media and platforms and their role in the (digital) world.
